{"type": "article", "id": 58559, "title": "它是边桌，也是猫咪的玩具｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-11-21T22:54:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 54451, "name": "Project Watches"}, {"id": 16881, "name": "Bang&Olufsen"}, {"id": 3255, "name": "Menu"}, {"id": 54452, "name": "MoFFan"}, {"id": 54453, "name": "Alessio Romano"}, {"id": 54454, "name": "Weihan He"}, {"id": 54455, "name": "Rigardt Greyling"}, {"id": 54456, "name": "RuiQiong Huang"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 121, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181121182535NQ8a1nbWorcIO6j9.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #dd4b39; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #dd4b39} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; background-color: #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3> “THEN” Side Table by RuiQiong Huang for MoFFan</h3><p>需要猫咪陪伴的人类越来越多，很多设计师在设计家具的时候也不再只考虑人的需求，而是更多地关注到了猫。比如这款名为 THEN 的边桌，出自设计师 RuiQiong Huang 之手，意在创造一处猫咪喜爱的舒适场所。</p><p>它设计得像一个迷你迷宫，为猫咪提供了一个游戏和休息的场所，同时也可以作为一个边桌，置于沙发旁或者是床边。顶部的内置开口允许猫在里面玩耍，同时还能将头探出来与主人互动，是很适合放在小空间里的互动家具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182601qELS6loiRhgfn8xb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182604G2tacs05uWgY3qUT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182604msxF067tAiOGMHrR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/11/14/furniture-for-furballs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Échasse Vase by Menu</h3><p>丹麦设计品牌 Menu 推出的这款名为 Échasse 的花瓶，像是一组穿着高跟鞋的花瓶。</p><p>据称，Échasse 的设计灵感，源自实验室中的试管，经典的水滴形状赋予它独特的表现力，一个类似高跷的金色金属架，将圆形底部的花瓶固定在桌子上。淋漓的波纹“荡漾于墙面、地面，与空间、光影呼应，一款配件，就可以提升空间氛围。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182703jl062CVwTvMB7415.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182705GyNkxom0JUvBXZF8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201811211827050w4UhsIifYxq2LEO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182711DWfpJ0PLru9Ntvym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://menu.as/en/website/accesories/echasse-vases/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Menu</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>ZERO Bluetooth Speaker by Rigardt Greyling</h3><p>以设计感著称的丹麦音响品牌 Bang&amp;Olufsen 的新项目，是请来几位设计师设计便携式蓝牙音箱，展示他们的设计才华，前提是建立在 B&amp;O 声学设计原理的研究基础之上，搭配合适的设计细节，确保最终产品在美学层面能够令人感到愉悦。</p><p>Zero 是一款便携式蓝牙扬声器，它有着一个俏皮的豆荚样式，由圆柱形磨砂玻璃外壳和耐用的茉莉酮酸脂材质的球体构成，置于镀铜框架中。干净简约的外观保留了微妙的小细节。</p><p>Zero 使用单个旋转拨盘打开蓝牙功能并调节音量，为用户提供快速简便的控制系统。扬声器由 1500mAh 锂离子电池供电，续航时间达 8 小时，并可使用 micro-usb 线缆在 2 小时内完成充电。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182758BnM5NSrxbZpYlKGt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182759ck87XP5hVJYjoC6M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182800B1PZrfyR8d3OJQFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666786\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182801ZpJIXwWx0FktycSa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666786\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182801nE0bOs7pr1hWqalc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182802HLs18ZJXIoTPRqVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/71463005/ZERO-Bluetooth-Speaker\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Sleevase by Weihan He</h3><p>养植鲜花、插花的过程中你可能会遇到花茎过长过短的问题，修剪起来很麻烦。为此，设计师 Weihan He 创造了一款花瓶，名为 Sleevase。</p><p>这款花瓶是设计师受到将衬衫的袖子卷起来的启发，并将其造型巧妙的运用到花瓶上而构成。花瓶使用了一种非常容易折叠的柔性材料，可以按照插花的长短来进行高低的调整。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182946t7msRQ2wKWZN4LV3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182946udB7wZWrURYGjVIm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182948iUmyLgFoEWlsNt0a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182948lawsINDhgiSFVT3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182949OZNxVqos4i1nrPLl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182950MKL3Qop7iJwS8NlC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.851429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121182950dSrBZ2mN0GKW7zjH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/11/16/formalwear-for-flowers/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Optical Watch by Alessio Romano for Project Watches</h3><p>Projects 来自于美国，成立三十年以来，以二十世纪建筑为标志性设计，带来了一种全新的时间表述形式，让人眼前一亮，就同官网上写的那句话一样：Architecture You Can Wear.</p><p>最近，设计师 Alessio Romano 为 Projects 设计了一款名为 Optical 的手表。这款手表配有两个催眠般的指针，并配有平行线图形。</p><p>Romano 深受 Victor Vasarely，Bridget Riley 和 Richard Anuszkiewicz 等艺术家作品的影响，他意在通过时针和分针的运动，创造出一种不断变化的视觉错觉，于是设计了这款光学手表。</p><p>为了保持手表外观的艺术性，表盘上也没有数字标记，为神秘感和好奇心都留有余地。售价 140 美元，<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Optical-Watch-Blue-Projects-Watches/dp/B01CQ0931S/ref=sr_1_4?tag=yankodesign05-20&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1540412454&amp;sr=8-4&amp;keywords=project+optical+watch\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121183220LOdyQp9oRmBK2nEY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121183221FMqIns7oXEd9A34G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121183222HVguyAEtjeoMIra4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121183222FEd8abhK4Po1QiSU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121183223S4MTq8e5lDwJKHOv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181121183223pV34JOHdLZmu9CQR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}